{"tid":548251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日日新鮮】海航再尋求延期償還啟德土地貸款","createTime":"2018-02-02T10:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T11:17:59.000Z","uid":147314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"93b3693ce3e8e1cec4f9bdde2c5c87382daa0576","tid":548251,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180202/s00002/1517559517637\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180202%2Fs00002%2F1517559517637&d=FP6j%2BlSK78%2FwI6t89AQszP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f3066898\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180202%2Fs00002%2F1517559517637&h=f00ad1f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180202/s00002/1517559517637</a><br />\n<br />\n【航程受阻】市傳海航再尋求延期償還啟德土地貸款<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180202/s00002/57f486c2fd6d84a93821835762c8350f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180202%2Fs00002%2F57f486c2fd6d84a93821835762c8350f.jpg&h=61e32c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n頻傳出現償債資金缺口的海航集團，彭博引述消息人士表示，旗下的香港國際建投（0687）正在與銀行商討再次延後其首筆的香港地產過橋貸款還款期。該筆貸款的現存餘額為28億元，整筆貸款原定需於去年11月償還，不過公司償還7億元後，獲延期一次至2月23日。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，香港國際建設尚未向銀行提交正式的延期計劃書，不過已經雙方已開始商討。如果海航不能再延期，貸款人有權取得土地控制權。海航拒絕置評。<br />\n<br />\n海航集團於啟德以272億元取得4幅土地，公司早前指第二筆過貸款已獲延期至7月15日，消息人士指第三和第四筆貸款將於2月和6月到期。早前市傳海航罕有地將2幅土地的發展注入基金，尋求外部投資者參與，每名投資最少100萬。"},{"pid":"1a906859e481442510a9fe16aa44d42f9510be27","tid":548251,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:37:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1759897/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F1759897%2F&d=FP6j%2BlSK78%2FwI6t89AQszP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4a7a7641\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/1759897/</a><br />\n<br />\n海航傳尋求啟德地第一筆貸款再延期<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/02/02/1759897_9737c067905a27986f31e6cda5feb4da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F02%2F02%2F1759897_9737c067905a27986f31e6cda5feb4da.jpg&h=cccc7cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外電引述知情人士透露，海航集團的一家子公司正與銀行商談，希望能夠再次推遲一筆貸款的償還日期。這筆貸款是海航為啟德地所借的第一筆過橋貸款。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士稱，各家銀行正與香港國際投資集團商談，不過該公司尚未正式申請貸款延期。如果海航不能獲得延期而又不能償還貸款，債權人有權接管地皮。<br />\n<br />\n海航在2016年底起，先後合共以272億元投得4幅啟德發展區地皮，期間曾籌組多筆過橋貸款。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士表示，上述商談集中在第一筆過橋貸款，在11月份償還了7億元，並延期至2月23日後，現在未償還餘額為28億元。海航此前表示，已經將第二筆過橋貸款延長6個月，至7月15日。"},{"pid":"4edd563c1d2ef47c3b2b54ef5c6727aef55272e8","tid":548251,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99d3d9eea613c3cdafc06948555bf3b4211e97ee","tid":548251,"uid":25116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a130ed5fa45bad164061f14378166d11c3dbaca","tid":548251,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932c5eaa9435d24aca76f24de7e768a1a5f6572e","tid":548251,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a130ed5fa45bad164061f14378166d11c3dbaca","tid":548251,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"460fe9b4f158830e40ac65cca17dec91e98003ee","tid":548251,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:57:49.000Z","msg":"支爆來了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a3261dc2142a3feb1db0a8b89b20e675b0515d","tid":548251,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"航爆"},{"pid":"97bcbcf656d3360cf2d6702d55694cf10c1b4094","tid":548251,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"希望海航爆煲<br />\n再引發支爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}